title: Video: Autre Ne Veut – Counting (feat. Mykki Blanco)
body: **[Mykki Blanco](http://admin.crackintheroad.com/music/18285-new-mykki-blanco-kingpinning-ice-cold-prod-by-brenmar/ "New: Mykki Blanco – Kingpinning (Ice Cold) (Prod. by Brenmar)")** has been busy this year. He released his debut Mixtape, _Cosmic Angel: The Illuminati Prince/ss_, shot a load of videos, and ends the year in the form of this featuring credit on the **[Autre Ne Veut](https://www.facebook.com/AutreNeVeut)** track, _Counting_. If anything is shows off his versatility, sounding like the late **Tupac** at times, I kid you not. The whole thing comes off a bit like that **[How to Dress Well//Active Child](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aO3COzIGr1U)** collab at times; passionate, story driven and sincere.
